Well, here is another point to think about. What do you do when the friends list is depleted? There is a post titled &quot;the server is dieing&quot;. It covers exactly that issue. <br>
<br>
&lt;&lt;, but it's also somewhat more realistic.&gt;&gt;<br>
<br>
Dieing and going to your bind point is not realistic, consuming food without ever eating is not realistic, Zoning to escape a mob is not realistic, elevators in Gfay with no mechanism, no maintenance are not realistic. Realism is often overlooked because of game machanics, requirements. <br>
<br>
A game that requires grouping as its core, yet does not have a practical means by which to accomplish this task as its core design is a game with a major design flaw. No?<br>
<br>
